The following three-part chronology, organized by location, has been
compiled primarily from exhibition checklists, press releases,
purchase receipts, grant reports, correspondence, exhibition reviews,
and other materials in the unprocessed Just Above Midtown Gallery
Records, Collection Linda Goode Bryant, New York (hereafter JAM
Records). Although every effort was made to determine the opening and
closing dates of exhibitions, in some cases only the opening dates
could be ascertained. The capitalization and punctuation of program
titles have been standardized. At times the titles are accompanied by
short quotations from archival documents. The page numbers following
program titles indicate the locations of related illustrations.
